  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your body is falling apart, forcing you to rely on mechanical augmentations or replacements to keep yourself alive. You take 1 point of Constitution damage each day, but you also ignore the first point of Strength, Dexterity, or Constitution damage you take for the remainder of that day.</p>\n<p>At 5th level, you gain a +2 bonus on all saving throws on effects that cause ability damage, ability drain, or ability score penalties.</p>\n<p>At 10th level, this bonus increases to +6.</p>\n<p>At 15th level, any effect that would normally deal ability drain on you instead deals ability damage whenever you successfully save against the effect.</p>",
